Additionally, the use of unconstrained face detection datasets suggests that it could belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper also discusses the performance of the proposed method compared to other face detection algorithms, which suggests that it could belong to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
